pageContext.description: Dimensions: EL 87mm; We 14.7mm; Ds 57.5mm,Typology: deep collar - prob. near flat orig.; gouge facet was prob. skew to cg. fls.; flattened top to mouth,Manufacture: most of cg. fl. evident (as stump, slight lipping); odd pmks. on body poss. ancient,Condition: most of edge good - quite sharp; crushing of body and consequent cracking at mouth ancient; apparently little modern interference
